ttp://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/review/2018/sep/21/mitron-movie-review-a-hit-and-a-miss-kind-of-film-1875355.html</ref> and in [[Malayalam]] as ''[[Vijay Superum Pournamiyum]]'' (2019).<ref>http://www.sify.com/movies/vijay-superum-pournamiyum-review-a-watchable-romantic-comedy-review-malayalam-tbmn9bhicabje.html</ref> In 2016, [[Gautham Menon]] bought the remake rights for [[Tamil language|Tamil]],<ref>https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/celebrities/story/pelli-choopulu-tamil-remake-rights-acquired-by-gautham-menon-348659-2016-10-26</ref> but the version, titled ''Pon Ondru Kandein'', failed to take off.<ref>https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/regional-cinema/story/vishnu-vishal-tamannaah-pelli-choopulu-remake-shelved-gautham-menon-reveals-1289983-2018-07-19</ref> The film is being remade in Tamil by debutante Kaarthikk Sundar starring [[Harish Kalyan]] and [[Priya Bhavani Shankar]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thehindu.com/entertainment/movies/harish-kalyan-to-star-in-pelli-choopulu-tamil-remake/article30275260.ece|title=Harish Kalyan to star in \u2018Pelli Choopulu\u2019 Tamil remake|date=11 December 2019|work=The Hindu|author=Pradeep Kumar}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* {{IMDb title|5824826}}\n\n{{National Film Award Best Feature Film Telugu|state=collapsed}}\n{{Filmfare Best Telugu Film}}\n\n[[Category:2016 films]]\n[[Category:2010s Telugu-language films]]\n[[Category:Films shot in Telangana]]\n[[Category:Indian romantic drama films]]\n[[Category:Films about Indian weddings]]\n[[Category:Telugu films remade in other languages]]\n[[Category:Films whose writer won the Best Dialogue National Film Award]]\n[[Category:Best Telugu Feature Film National Film Award winners]]\n[[Category:Indian films]]\n[[Category:2016 directorial debut films]]\n", "name_user": "122.183.47.212", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pelli_Choopulu"}
